{"tid":1602704,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日有份捉鬼/屌過既人入黎","createTime":"2019-09-29T13:19:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T13:31:46.000Z","uid":4044,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2b73aee935fc24f4b51606bf4877090ac680506c","tid":1602704,"uid":4044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:19:12.000Z","msg":"以下內容只係玩香城online <br />\n<br />\n借朋友ac：我就係喊果個絲打/巴打嘅手足<br />\n我哋下次都唔會再帶燈<br />\n但問題係 我哋啲身型無一個似鬼<br />\n捉鬼都用下腦<br />\n知道好多年輕嘅巴絲都有幫我哋 多謝你哋 <br />\n問題係 講曬我哋係狗死全家<br />\n有手足俾曬Id 有手足俾曬學生證<br />\n禮貌地同你哋解釋或者無視你哋<br />\n都仲係今俾人跟 俾人影<br />\n屌到我哋絲打巴打喊曬<br />\n加上我地一早買定紅燈你估我地想架<br />\n希望你哋唔好擺我哋啲相同片出黎<br />\n100日過左 大家都真係好攰<br />\n希望大家識救人 唔係淨係識捉鬼<br />\n十一希望大家再企出黎 唔帶標<br />\n全民玩魔法師 全民勇武<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yU85Qfd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyU85Qfd.jpg&h=63346002&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lbj45OB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLbj45OB.jpg&h=eec241dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fe42410d767bf021129a0e686b57ed25de90417a","tid":1602704,"uid":71713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:19:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e318004b2ace161dc0608b1f5a557d0c47312cf","tid":1602704,"uid":6111,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:21:28.000Z","msg":"根本一早就唔應該帶係身<br />\n明知同狗d記認咁似都帶住係身<br />\n咁比人懷疑都好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0bd7a19ee15483dfa9f4bb618f0fd9dcf1c5aff","tid":1602704,"uid":278201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e318004b2ace161dc0608b1f5a557d0c47312cf","tid":1602704,"uid":6111,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:21:28.000Z","msg":"根本一早就唔應該帶係身<br />\n明知同狗d記認咁似都帶住係身<br />\n咁比人懷疑都好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sos